Action: Shuffle each IDR independently preserving exact AA composition
Purpose: Negative control for sequence composition bias
Seed:   99
Inputs:
  - 00-raw/autism-idrs-clean.fasta (1502 seqs)
  - 01-control-data/control-idrs-clean.fasta (1130 seqs)
Outputs:
